- A server is a computer that provides resources and services to other computers.
- Usually installed with specialized software(thw đc cài đặt phần mềm chuyên dụng) to be able to provide
- Server with high configuration(cấu hình cao), stable performance
- A server can be used for one or more purposes. The hostname(tên máy chủ) is usually associated with the intended(mục đích) use.

For example:
 File server
 Application server
 Mail server
 Web server
